## Authentication Flow

```
Register
    │
    ▼
Login
    │
    ▼
JWT Access Token
    │
    ▼
API Requests
    │
    ▼
Access Token Expires
    │
    ▼
Refresh Token
    │
    ▼
New Access Token
```

